title: On Yer Bike with the Volcom UK team
description:
Kris Vile and Harry Lintell spent a few days playing London's public cycle hire scheme to their advantage, keeping the cost of travel in the city to a minimum whilst keeping the hit rate of spots high. Check out the video clip from the ride around town and make sure you go buy the new Kingpin to read the article.

- Music -

Song: "Rad Times"
Artist: Black Bananas
Release: Rad Times Xpress IV
